3.5 DSSD front-back Correlation(II) - dssd1¶

  • 对x-y的所有条进行能量刻度 (幅度归一化)
  • 学习进行复杂分析的思路和方法

3.4节回顾¶

  • 粒子在入射位置为：xstrip = i条、ystrip = j条，标记为$(x_i, y_j)$

  • 对于入射到 $(x_i,y_j)$ ，能量沉积为E的粒子: $A_{x_i} = K_{x_iy_j}A_{y_j} + B_{x_iy_j} $

幅度归一化的目标是，将y侧所有条相对于参考条$x_i$条进行归一。¶

方法1¶

  • 固定参考条 $x_i$ 条不变，按照上述方程依次遍历所有的 $y_j$ 条, 得到 y 侧的归一化系数：

  • $A_{x_i} = K_{x_iy_j}A_{x_j} + B_{x_iy_j} \to $ $\lbrace K_{x_i,y_j},B_{x_i,y_j}\rbrace \quad ,y_j=0,1,...N_y $

  • 利用上一步骤得到的系数，对 y 侧所有条进行刻度：$\lbrace A'_{y_j} = K_{x_i,y_j}A_{y_j} + B_{x_i,y_j} \rbrace\quad ,j=0,1,...N_y$。

  • 以刻度后 y 侧某一条 $y_j$ 条作为参考条，对所有 x 侧的条进行刻度 $ A'_{y_j}=K_{y_j,x_i}A_{x_i} + B_{y_j,x_i}$

经上述步骤，DSSD的 $x$ 和 $y$ 的所有条能量都归一化到第$i$参考条

  • 该方法利用的是每个x条和每个y条重叠区域事件(pixel), 前提是入射到每一个$(x_i,y_j)$ pixel的粒子有足够的统计。

方法2¶

  • 更充分利用 x-y 侧的关联关系

  1. 在 x 侧和 y 侧分别寻找统计最高的条$(x_{i_m},y_{j_m})$

  2. 以$x_{i_m}$为参考条，刻度y侧一系列条： $y_{j_{m-k_1}},. ,y_{j_m},.,y_{j_{m+k_2}}$ , 要求这些组合有足够的统计。

  3. 以刻度后的$y_{j_{m-k_1}},. ,y_{j_m},.,y_{j_{m+k_2}}$ 为参考条，刻度 $x_{i_{m-k_3}},.,x_{i_m},.,x_{i_{m+k_4}}$, 要求这些组合有足够的统计。

  4. 按照上述步骤向外推进，直到最外边缘的条的正背面关联有足够的统计做拟合。

拟合步骤¶

  • 观察不同能量范围的iy-ix关联图，得到如下拟合步骤
  1. 选择 xm = 16 作为参考条，拟合得到g[16][8:16]范围的刻度系数 - gFit("Y",g)
  2. 用上述刻度系数，刻度g[0:31][8:16]的y轴，合并y轴，存到gxc[0:31] - CalibrateAndMerge("Y",8,16,ic), ic:0-31
  3. 拟合gxc[0:31]，得到[0:31]范围的x轴刻度系数 - gFit("X",gxc)
  4. 用上述刻度系数，刻度g[0:31][0:31]的x轴，合并x轴，存到gyc[0:31] - CalibrateAndMerge("X",0,31,ic), ic:0-31
  5. 拟合gyc[0:31]，得到[0:31]范围的y轴刻度系数 - gFit("Y",gyc)
  6. 用上述刻度系数，刻度g[0:31][0:31]的y轴，合并y轴，存到gxc[0:31] - CalibrateAndMerge("Y",0,31,ic), ic:0-31
  7. 拟合gxc[0:31]，得到[0:31]范围的x轴刻度系数 - gFit("X",gxc)

gFit¶

  • IsXY = "X": fit g(x,y) with y=k*x+b, i.e. calibrate x using y as the standard
  • IsXY = "Y": fit g(x,y) with x=k*y+b, i.e. calibrate y using x as the standard
  • g: graph to be fitted
  • hres: residual 2d-histogram
  • par[3] for TF2
  • stat[3]: ymin,ymax,Ncout for fitting
  • minCount: minimum count for TGraph fitting
In [9]:
bool gFit(char IsXY, TGraph *g, TH2F *hres, double* par, double &chi2ndf, int *sta,int minCount=20)
{    
    //cout<<g->GetN()<<endl;
    if(g->GetN() < minCount)
        return 0;
    TGraph *g1 = new TGraph;
    TGraph *g2 = new TGraph;
    TF1 *fpa1 = new TF1("fp1","pol1",200,8000);
    TF1 *fpa2 = new TF1("fp2","pol2",200,8000);
    int ymin = 10000, ymax = 0;
    double par1[2];
    for(int k=0; k<g->GetN(); k++) {
            double x = g->GetX()[k];
            double y = g->GetY()[k];
            if(IsXY == 'Y' or IsXY == 'y') swap(x,y);//x=ky+b
            g1->SetPoint(k,x,y);
    }
    g1->Fit(fpa1,"Q ROB");
    fpa1->GetParameters(&par1[0]);
    int ng = 0;
    for(int k=0; k<g1->GetN(); k++) {
            double x = g1->GetX()[k];
            double y = g1->GetY()[k];
            if (abs(y-(par1[0]+par1[1]*x))<20) { //eliminate outliers
                g2->SetPoint(ng,x,y);
                ng++;
            }           
    }
    if(g2->GetN() >= minCount) {
        g2->Fit(fpa2,"Q");
        fpa2->GetParameters(&par[0]);
        chi2ndf=fpa2->GetChisquare()/fpa2->GetNDF();
        for(int j = 0;j < g2->GetN(); j++){
            double x = g2->GetX()[j];
            double y = g2->GetY()[j];
            hres->Fill(par[0]+par[1]*x+par[2]*x*x-y,y);
            if(y > ymax) ymax = y;
            if(y < ymin) ymin = y;
        }
    }
    sta[0] = ymin;
    sta[1] = ymax;
    sta[2] = g2->GetN();
    delete fpa1;
    delete fpa2;
    delete g1;
    delete g2;
    if(sta[2] < minCount) 
        return 0;
    else 
        return 1;    
}

CalibrateAndMerge¶

  • Calibrate & Merge xstrips
  • IsXY ='X' calibrate & merge xstrips within the range of m1 to m2
    • ic: ystrip
    • gc: merged & calibrated graph : g[m1:m2][ic] -> gyc[ic]
      • ic indicates the index of y-strip in gyc[ic]
  • IsXY ='Y' calibrate & merge ystrips within the range of m1 to m2
    • ic: xstrip
    • gc: merged & calibrated graph for g[ic][m1:m2] ->gxc[ic] -ic indicates the index of x-strip in gxc[ic]
In [13]:
void CalibrateAndMerge(char IsXY,int m1,int m2, int ic, TGraph *gc)
{
    gc->Clear();
    int ngy = 0;
    if(IsXY == 'X') {
        for(int ix=m1; ix<=m2; ix++) {
            for(int i=0; i<g[ix][ic]->GetN(); i++) {
                double x = g[ix][ic]->GetX()[i];
                double y = g[ix][ic]->GetY()[i];
                x = parx[ix][0] + parx[ix][1] * x + parx[ix][2] * x * x;
                gc->SetPoint(ngy, x, y);
                ngy++;
            }
        }
    }
    else {
        for(int iy=m1; iy<=m2; iy++) {
            for(int i=0; i<g[ic][iy]->GetN(); i++) {
                double x = g[ic][iy]->GetX()[i];
                double y = g[ic][iy]->GetY()[i];
                y = pary[iy][0] + pary[iy][1] * y + pary[iy][2] * y * y;
                gc->SetPoint(ngy,x,y);
                ngy++;
            }
        }        
    }
}

TH2F *hresall = new TH2F("hresall","hresall",100,-50,50,1000,200,8000);
TH2F *hxy = new TH2F("hxy","hxy",1000,200,8000,1000,200,8000);
TH2F *hxycal = new TH2F("hxycal","hxycal",1000,200,8000,1000,200,8000);
hresall->Reset();
for(int ix=0; ix<32; ix++) {
   for(int iy=0; iy<32; iy++) {
    for(int i=0; i<g[ix][iy]->GetN(); i++) {
        double x = g[ix][iy]->GetX()[i];
        double y = g[ix][iy]->GetY()[i];
        hxy->Fill(x, y);
        x = parx[ix][0] + parx[ix][1] * x + parx[ix][2] * x * x;
        y = pary[iy][0] + pary[iy][1] * y + pary[iy][2] * y * y;
        hxycal->Fill(x, y);
        hresall->Fill(x-y, y);
    }
   }
}
hresall->Draw("colz");
c1->Draw();
